      <Meanings>
        <Meaning id="2c29fb51-c09b-4104-a6a1-0d0508797c9d" type="Noun">
          <Vi>con voi</Vi>
          <En>A large, heavy mammal with a long trunk, large ears, and long curved tusks; the largest living land animal.</En>
          <Example>Elephants are highly intelligent and social animals that live in matriarchal herds.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="90970b63-61c5-479d-8f14-41be7a1df6e4">
              <Vi>Mô tả loài động vật có vú lớn, sống thành đàn ở châu Phi và châu Á.</Vi>
              <En>Describing the large, tusked, trunked mammal found in Africa and Asia.</En>
            </Situation>
            <Situation id="e74a6494-dd56-48a7-9595-b0ca239ffb41">
              <Vi>Trong các công viên quốc gia, du khách thường chiêm ngưỡng đàn voi hoang dã.</Vi>
              <En>In national parks, tourists often observe wild elephant herds.</En>
            </Situation>
